      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in pristine, showroom condition, having been maintained to the most exacting standards. Every surface reflects a commitment to excellence, offering the discerning collector or enthusiast a rare opportunity to acquire a truly superlative example of its marque. We invite rigorous inspection to confirm its status as a benchmark of its class.",
