    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve cherished this car and kept it tucked away in the garage, so it's still looking and driving like a dream. It\u2019s super clean, incredibly reliable, and ready for a new home. I'm so excited for the next owner to get behind the wheel\u2014drop me a message if you want to come check it out!",
