    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy. This car is seriously in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it still feels like it just rolled off the lot! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, always kept in the garage, and drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been loved and looks practically brand new, you\u2019ve found it! I'd love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43500.0,
