    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3, maintained to an exacting standard. This specimen features the S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response, mated to a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. The mechanical integrity is absolute: the rod bearing service is documented, the dual-VANOS system has been overhauled with upgraded seals, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced to ensure structural rigidity. The chassis retains factory-spec kinematics with fresh bushings and OE-damped suspension. Finished in Carbon Black with an immaculate Cinnamon Nappa leather interior, the cabin ergonomics remain as crisp as the day it left Regensburg. This is a turn-key, high-revving masterpiece for the discerning driver who values mechanical transparency and performance purity.",
